for you to see, OK?

95
00:12:41,657 --> 00:12:45,235
Just watch me!
One, two, one, two.

96
00:12:45,374 --> 00:12:46,908
Attention!

97
00:12:48,104 --> 00:12:49,754
Little darling, let Uncle Chen hold you.

98
