103
00:13:21,699 --> 00:13:24,290
'He's got bad breath, don't let him kiss you, don't let him.'

104
00:13:28,019 --> 00:13:29,959
Ugh, lots of little hairs.

105
00:13:30,981 --> 00:13:35,175
